This paper deals with online content recommendation, which is a problem commonly studied in the machine learning and artificial intelligence communities. The use of pairwise comparisons and the dueling bandit problem is also a common topic in machine learning research. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
